{"tid":2296461,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"高登巴打爆炸頭同埋廚房巴第一次公開亮相","createTime":"2020-11-22T13:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T11:56:01.000Z","uid":162724,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b69ad4352510b9d9377aa52fc3743ea9b8b4d082","tid":2296461,"uid":162724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:21:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NSOL6eBpLRo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNSOL6eBpLRo&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT8IAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=da3c87f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NSOL6eBpLRo</a><br />\n<br />\n由香港電台頭條新聞原班人馬製作新節目【港食力】，首次攝錄了高登巴打爆炸頭及廚房巴。一年前,兩位在理大戰場中各自堅守自己的崗位。一年過後，兩位的生活又發生了什麼變化？<br />\n<br />\nP.S 廚房巴留咗言，有咩係嗰度搵佢啦。<br />\n<br />\n同埋多謝兩位當初的貢獻和付出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf404da0f16f642b85cf7b28811453618e6704e5","tid":2296461,"uid":162724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:21:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf92fce767e9bc1f4d4f8b46953f5c86cd355aee","tid":2296461,"uid":162724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:21:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f3ab533ef6ed7b589aedd97690a9621c46bc428","tid":2296461,"uid":162724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:22:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6331c909fbb14121e597bb47579ee722e3c610de","tid":2296461,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:07:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"198046934645eafb56a2cb08d95ea9c1ae4d64e0","tid":2296461,"uid":162724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:59:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4afac44e7538f074c74d550d5e53f42353de629","tid":2296461,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T15:00:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b9b4ed3178834783dc71cc36e88e2244cab3590","tid":2296461,"uid":162724,"like"